title: French parliament passes tough asylum bill
text:
French parliament passes tough asylum bill 6:11am EDT - 00:52 
France's parliament has passed an immigration law that has caused widespread unease, after a debate that overran through the weekend and opened rifts within President Emmanuel Macron's party. Lucy Fielder reports.
